588
00:29:29,620 --> 00:29:31,050
You have to figure it out for yourself.

589
00:29:32,980 --> 00:29:33,860
Lan,

590
00:29:34,110 --> 00:29:35,920
if it were you,

591
00:29:36,380 --> 00:29:37,820
