00:30:25,920 --> 00:30:26,460
Aren't there really

608
00:30:26,550 --> 00:30:28,490
any other treatments?

609
00:30:33,320 --> 00:30:35,190
With the current treatment method...

610
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:40,420
How long can

611
00:30:41,580 --> 00:30:43,210
my grandpa live?

