00:30:46,450 --> 00:30:47,530
Two months.

614
00:31:24,230 --> 00:31:25,140
Si Nian.

615
00:31:25,460 --> 00:31:26,690
I'm here to see grandpa.

616
00:31:27,350 --> 00:31:28,230
Thank you.

