629
00:32:17,710 --> 00:32:19,250
Go... Go overseas?

630
00:32:21,380 --> 00:32:22,340
Of course.

631
00:32:24,980 --> 00:32:26,560
Why don't you discuss it?

632
00:32:27,070 --> 00:32:29,240
I'll come back to see
grandpa in a couple of days.

633
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:32,040
Okay.

634
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,370
Then I'll go first.

635
00:32:34,520 --> 00:32:35,400
Thank you.

